    <title>工作笔记</title>
    <url>/20230216/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>#工作<br>
看《unity动作游戏开发实战》<br>
DNLSprite_Normal   line-&gt; 223<br>
shader 写在  Sprite-DNL.shader</p>
<p>配置Git Bash使用SSH协议3步：</p>
<ol>
<li>生成SSH Key：打开Git Bash，运行以下命令：</li>
</ol>
<p><code>$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096 -C &quot;your_email@example.com&quot;</code></p>
<p>然后按提示输入密码和文件的存储路径。</p>
<ol start="2">
<li>添加SSH Key到ssh-agent：运行以下命令：</li>
</ol>
<p><code>$ eval &quot;$(ssh-agent -s)&quot; $ ssh-add ~/.ssh/id_rsa</code><br>
然后Github那边添加SSH</p>
<p>Hexo安装<br>
安装nodejs，npm安装<br>
npm install -g hexo-cli<br>
就可以启动项目了<br>
hexo s --debug  本地测试<br>
hexo g -d 部署到github</p>
<p>npm install hexo-tag-dplayer -s<br>
npm install hexo-tag-aplayer -s</p>
<div style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 0; padding-bottom: 75%;">
<iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=831027623&bvid=BV1J34y1P7FY&cid=1270320148&p=1&high_quality=1&danmaku=0" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true" style="position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; left: 0; top: 0;"> </iframe>
</div>
<p>#云际<br>
21楼是律师事务所<br>
9楼是婚纱的<br>
安迪推荐了  鱼油  21金维他   善存 买多维</p>
<p>UI界面资源脚本 CollectUISprites.cs<br>
UIFrame-生成代码MonoScript到预制体的引用<br>
IGameTools-&gt;TextureImportSetting 批量设置图片格式<br>
GlobalNetMessage -&gt; Line 356 是新手引导相关<br>
服务器5人<br>
系统5人<br>
战斗4人<br>
引擎7~8人<br>
自己写一个框架  包含AB包资源加载<br>
Update轮询，对象池管理<br>
Editor有专门的EditorPrefs存数据</p>
<p>TMGeNode.PushCommand 压入命令   在update时候轮询再按需求执行<br>
FB表格处理  NPOI读写xls + FlatBuffer序列化<br>
Animation<br>
BattleLogic<br>
Framework_Recycle  FrameStack<br>
UIFramework</p>
<p>神陵武装<br>
动物大联盟<br>
勇闯地下城<br>
街机三国<br>
暗夜格斗<br>
DNF Extractor 提取资源<br>
#性能优化<br>
数据Init之类的  都只是传入数据，而不执行Init方法。等该执行的时候才去执行<br>
粒子转序列帧贴图播放<br>
2D角色转RBG通道然后从key取色，分层  ，每个通道的颜色代表调色盘第几位，第0位必须是空颜色。 渲染是靠自己写shader和材质。<br>
DNLAtlasElement里 rect去合图里截取方块，然后pivot记录这个方块在实际渲染的偏移。通过原图在旧的500x500的图的中心点偏移量获得。这个pivot对应Sprite.Create时的pivot<br>
mat.SetVector(DNLSpriteShader.PROPERTYID_CHANNELMASK)</p>
<p>图片打包是用 github -&gt; juj / RectangleBinPack<br>
shadow是用原图渲染到地上，并且只有某几个部分有投影<br>
重写unity的image UI 通过OnPopulateMesh 重新绘制mesh的形状<br>
AStar 的OpenList用MinHeap  Heap是堆<br>
AABB不可以旋转     OBB可以旋转<br>
项目UI框架gameframework写的MVC   view 和frame分开<br>
用数组模拟最大堆<br>
用scriptObject存储数据，实际runtime转为二进制<br>
DelayCaller.cs<br>
乱世的UI框架<br>
Unitask<br>
TextAnimation<br>
Animancer<br>
Odin<br>
状态机<br>
自己写一些摄像机跟随代替pro camera 2d<br>
使用BetterStreamingAsset读取streamingAsset资源<br>
Spine动画的导入<br>
按位运算<br>
LittleEndian</p>
<h2 id="LRU（Least-Recently-Used）最近最少使用算法">LRU（Least Recently Used）最近最少使用算法</h2>
<p>思想：最近被使用過的資料，那麼將來被訪問的概率也多，最近沒有被訪問，那麼將來被訪問的概率也比較低。<br>
如圖，P1到P7都有最後一次使用的時間，今天如果滿了，我們就淘汰最久沒被使用的，如圖的P7。<br>
但這想法並不考慮頻率，所以會有問題，例如今天突然需要遍歷資料，那這個遍歷會將真正常用的資料淘汰出cache。<br>
![[Pasted image 20230315165931.png]]</p>
<p>c# LINQ</p>
<ul>
<li>Map,对应C#的Select</li>
<li>Filter,对应C#的Where</li>
<li>Fold,对应C#的Aggregate</li>
<li>FlattMap 对应 SelectMany</li>
</ul>
<p>png alpha color clear</p>
<figure class="highlight c#"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> UnityEngine;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> UnityEditor;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">PngAlphaClearColor</span> : <span class="title">EditorWindow</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> Texture2D texture2D;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="meta">MenuItem(<span class="string">&quot;Test/PngAlphaClearColor&quot;</span>)</span>]</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">ShowWindow</span>()</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        EditorWindow.GetWindow(<span class="keyword">typeof</span>(PngAlphaClearColor));</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">OnGUI</span>()</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        texture2D = EditorGUILayout.ObjectField(texture2D, <span class="keyword">typeof</span>(Texture2D), <span class="literal">false</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> Texture2D;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (GUILayout.Button(<span class="string">&quot;Test&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            Test();</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Test</span>()</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">string</span> path = AssetDatabase.GetAssetPath(texture2D);</span><br><span class="line">        TextureImporter ti = (TextureImporter)TextureImporter.GetAtPath(path);</span><br><span class="line">        ti.isReadable = <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        AssetDatabase.ImportAsset(path);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="built_in">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; texture2D.width; ++i)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="built_in">int</span> j = <span class="number">0</span>; j &lt; texture2D.height; ++j)</span><br><span class="line">            &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                Color color = texture2D.GetPixel(i, j);</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> (color.a == <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">                &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    texture2D.SetPixel(i, j, <span class="keyword">new</span> Color(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>));</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        System.IO.File.WriteAllBytes(path, texture2D.EncodeToPNG());</span><br><span class="line">        ti.isReadable = <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        AssetDatabase.ImportAsset(path);</span><br><span class="line">        AssetDatabase.Refresh();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
